widgets_values: A photo-realistic amateur image of a stunning 40-year-old woman with shoulder-length wavy honey-blonde hair pulled up in a messy bun, green eyes. She has a curvy yet fit body, toned waist, wide hips, wearing a fitted white tank top and grey yoga pants. She is standing in a dim, messy teenage boy's bedroom, holding up a black lace bra she just found. She's inspecting and looking at the bra with a disappointed and confused expression on her face. The room behind her has an unmade bed, a PC desk setup, clothes scattered around, decoration and posters on the wall. Afternoon light filters through drawn curtains, casting warm amber tones across the scene.

An 800x400 pixel banner in retro 8-bit pixel art style (like classic NES Super Mario Bros). A green warp pipe from Super Mario centered in the composition, viewed from a slight top-down 3/4 angle showing the dark circular opening at the top. The pipe is the iconic bright green (#30b030) with darker green shading on the sides and a wide cylindrical rim at the top, just like in the original NES games. Colorful pixel-art data particles (blue, orange, purple small squares) float into the pipe opening, suggesting data being warped/bundled. Solid dark navy/charcoal background (#1a1a2e). Clean pixel art aesthetic with visible blocky pixels, no anti-aliasing, crisp edges. No text, no characters, no ground tiles. Just the pipe and data particles on dark background. Simple, iconic, readable at small sizes.
